Little Ella JamesSince Sep 2011 / 2162 reviewsThis partner has a rating of 5 starsaboutproductsreviewsneed to knowAboutCurated Collection of Quality Childrens' Gifts'Little Ella James' is a handpicked collection of unique gifts for children's birthdays and parties.'Ella James' was launched by two sisters Ashley and Alison in 2009. After leaving London and careers in the city, the two sisters decided to fulfil a lifelong ambition of setting up a home interiors, accessories and online gift business together.With a passion for imaginative , quality products which make wonderful gifts, they set about sourcing the pieces for their ' Little Ella James' range in 2011, named after their two eldest children.The focus is on quality products sourced mainly from Europe which will become treasured pieces which will stand the test of time .Now in its fifth year , the childrens range has a following of loyal customers and has been featured in several major publications such as 'Living Etc' and 'Junior magazine'Like this partner?Share it on Share on Facebook Share on TwitterOur Productsview all products20% offThis is a product from Little Ella James named Baby Pom Pom HatBaby Pom Pom Hat£8£6.40This is a product from Little Ella James named Bloom Pink Teepee With Wooden Feather TrimBloom Pink Teepee With Wooden Feather Trim£18020% offThis is a product from Little Ella James named Hand Painted Wooden Bowling SetHand Painted Wooden Bowling Set£49£39.20This is a product from Little Ella James named Wooden Play Tool Bench And Tool KitWooden Play Tool Bench And Tool Kit£275This is a product from Little Ella James named Large Felt Race Track With Wooden CarLarge Felt Race Track With Wooden Car£7520% offThis is a product from Little Ella James named Wooden Dolls Classic Cot BedWooden Dolls Classic Cot Bed£130£10420% offThis is a product from Little Ella James named Vintage Rose Wooden Dolls PramVintage Rose Wooden Dolls Pram£155£12420% offThis is a product from Little Ella James named Grey