Product Reviews:




Add your own review of this item








By: Steve Greer | K&L Staff Member | Review Date: 9/7/2010 | Send Email

                I drank this with a friend over the weekend and really enjoyed it. The wine is 100% Grenache based on a 10 year Solera with 50% from the 2009 vintage and 50% from vintages back to 1999.

Bright raspberry and spice on the nose and palate. The palate was soft with lush fruit with a nice back-bone of acidity. 

Only $11.99. This wine is going to go quickly.
            








